    dc:creator "Zheng, Yuchen; Liu, Xingyue" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "First description of immature stages of the antlion Bullanga florida (Navás, 1913) (Neuroptera, Myrmeleontidae, Dendroleontini)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412508>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412512>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412510> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412508>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4–8. Bullanga florida (Navás, 1913), 3rd instar larva. 4. head, dorsal view; 5. head, ventral view; 6. thorax, dorsal view; 7. abdominal segments VII–IX, dorsal view; 8. abdominal segments VII–XI, ventral view. 1t: first tooth; 2t: second tooth; 3t: third tooth; Ims: interdental mandibular setae; D: dolichaster; Ms: mesothoracic spiracles; Ph: plumose hair; Msp: mesothoracic setiferous processes; Wdds: weakly developed digging setae; VIII-As: VIII abdominal spiracles. Scale bar: 2.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4412508/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412512>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–17. Habitats of Bullanga florida (Navás, 1913). 13. habitat I; 14. habitat II; 15. habitat III; 16. corpses of larva leftover in habitat III; 17. habitat IV. Red arrows indicate the positions where the larvae were collected; blue arrow indicates the position where the corpses were found in habitat III." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4412512/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4412510>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Biological photos of Bullanga florida in immature stages. 9. 3rd instar larva in habitat I; 10. 3rd instar larva feeding on woodlice (Porcellio sp.) in artificial feeding habitat; 11. cocoon; 12. pupa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4412510/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

